COMPANY PROFILE



Exponent, Inc.
CA, 

United StatesTel: (650) 688-7104Fax: 

(650) 688-7231
www.exponent.com

Click Here to Contact





Member Since 2016
Robotic Consultant






Member Since 2016
Robotic Consultant

Exponent is a multi-disciplinary engineering and scientific consulting firm that brings together more than 90 different disciplines to solve important engineering, science, regulatory, and business issues facing our clients. We are recognized for our integrity, objectivity, independence, and professionalism. For nearly 50 years, we have provided high quality consulting to corporations, insurance carriers, government agencies, and law firms worldwide. The firm originated analyzing accidents and failures to determine their causes, but has since expanded to include assisting with engineering, design, and regulatory analysis during the development of new products or processes. Our consultants are preeminent experts in their fields, and over 50% of our staff have a Ph.D. or M.D. With its roots in Silicon Valley, Exponent has offices located in the United States, Europe and China. 

Visit Website
Click Here to Contact






